# в”Җв”Җ 3. glance_view_band_catпјҡе’ҢDPHзҡ„е…ізі»в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
print("\n=== glance_view_band_cat vs in_stock_dph ===")
if "glance_view_band_cat" in df.columns:
    gv = df.groupby("glance_view_band_cat").agg(
        n=("asin", "count"),
        mean_instock=("in_stock_dph", "mean"),
        mean_demand=("fbi_demand", "mean"),
